<article id="post-5435" class="post-5435 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-ccmusic category-reviews tag-analog tag-engines tag-fans tag-guitar tag-machines tag-propellers tag-props tag-synth tag-white-noise has-post-thumbnail">
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://cerebralrift.org/2014/07/21/discover-the-aural-vessels/" title="Permalink to Discover The Aural Vessels" rel="bookmark">Discover The Aural Vessels</a></h1>
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

		<div class="entry-summary">
				<div class="featured-image">
			<a href="http://cerebralrift.org/2014/07/21/discover-the-aural-vessels/" title="Discover The Aural Vessels">
				<img width="280" height="280" src="http://cerebralrift.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Rui_P_Andrade__Vessels-280x280.jpg" class="attachment-half-width wp-post-image" alt="Discover The Aural Vessels" />			</a>
		</div>
		
		<p>When you discover the aural vessels of Rui Andrade you might find the beauty in noise you never considered to have any characteristics before.</p>
	</div><!-- .entry-summary -->
	
