<article id="post-5298" class="post-5298 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-ccmusic category-reviews tag-drone tag-fog tag-noise tag-retro tag-synthesis has-post-thumbnail">
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://cerebralrift.org/2014/07/03/in-retro-fog-with-kevin-krebs/" title="Permalink to In Retro Fog With Kevin Krebs" rel="bookmark">In Retro Fog With Kevin Krebs</a></h1>
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

		<div class="entry-summary">
				<div class="featured-image">
			<a href="http://cerebralrift.org/2014/07/03/in-retro-fog-with-kevin-krebs/" title="In Retro Fog With Kevin Krebs">
				<img width="280" height="280" src="http://cerebralrift.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/km_krebs__fog_sequences-280x280.jpg" class="attachment-half-width wp-post-image" alt="In Retro Fog With Kevin Krebs" />			</a>
		</div>
		
		<p>A stunning recording. I hadn&#8217;t experienced this kind of work since I left college. Let&#8217;s look in retro fog with Kevin Krebs to understand his mastery.</p>
	</div><!-- .entry-summary -->
	
	<footer class="entry-meta">
		<span class="posted-on icon-clock"><a href="http://cerebralrift.org/2014/07/03/in-retro-fog-with-kevin-krebs/" title="8:00 am" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-07-03T08:00:00+00:00">July 3, 2014</time></a></span> <span class="byline icon-user"><span class="post-author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://cerebralrift.org/author/George/" title="View all posts by Snd Chaser" rel="author">Snd Chaser</a></span></span>
		
		
